highlights.text: Olivia Rodrigo has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “good 4 u” is the highest at #1.
“Solar Power” by Lorde is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #25.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 228 weeks straight.
“GANG GANG (with Lil Wayne)” by Polo G and Lil Wayne is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 87 spots at #91.
